#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "mn7:5.32"
msgid "So buddhe aveccappasādena samannāgato hoti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn7:5.33"
msgid ""
"‘itipi so bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho vijjācaraṇasampanno sugato lokavidū "
"anuttaro purisadammasārathi satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavā’ti;"
msgstr ""

#. <a class="nya" id="nya6"></a>
msgctxt "mn7:6.1"
msgid "dhamme aveccappasādena samannāgato hoti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn7:6.2"
msgid ""
"‘svākkhāto bhagavatā dhammo sandiṭṭhiko akāliko ehipassiko opaneyyiko "
"paccattaṃ veditabbo viññūhī’ti;"
msgstr ""

#. <a class="nya" id="nya7"></a>
msgctxt "mn7:7.1"
msgid "saṅghe aveccappasādena samannāgato hoti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn7:7.2"
msgid ""
"‘suppaṭipanno bhagavato sāvakasaṅgho, ujuppaṭipanno bhagavato sāvakasaṅgho, "
"ñāyappaṭipanno bhagavato sāvakasaṅgho, sāmīcippaṭipanno bhagavato "
"sāvakasaṅgho, yadidaṃ cattāri purisayugāni, aṭṭha purisapuggalā. Esa "
"bhagavato sāvakasaṅgho āhuneyyo pāhuneyyo dakkhiṇeyyo añjalikaraṇīyo, "
"anuttaraṃ puññakkhettaṃ lokassā’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya8-11"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.38"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
#. VAR: Yathodhi → yatopi (bj) | yatodhi (aṭṭhakathāyaṃ pāṭhantaraṃ)
msgctxt "mn7:8-11.1"
msgid ""
"Yathodhi kho panassa cattaṃ hoti vantaṃ muttaṃ pahīnaṃ paṭinissaṭṭhaṃ, so ‘"
"buddhe aveccappasādena samannāgatomhī’ti labhati atthavedaṃ, labhati "
"dhammavedaṃ, labhati dhammūpasaṃhitaṃ pāmojjaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn7:8-11.2"
msgid ""
"Pamuditassa pīti jāyati, pītimanassa kāyo passambhati, passaddhakāyo sukhaṃ "
"vedeti, sukhino cittaṃ samādhiyati;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn7:8-11.3"
msgid "‘dhamme … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn7:8-11.4"
msgid ""
"saṃghe aveccappasādena samannāgatomhī’ti labhati atthavedaṃ, labhati "
"dhammavedaṃ, labhati dhammūpasaṃhitaṃ pāmojjaṃ;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn7:8-11.5"
msgid ""
"pamuditassa pīti jāyati, pītimanassa kāyo passambhati, passaddhakāyo sukhaṃ "
"vedeti, sukhino cittaṃ samādhiyati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn7:8-11.6"
msgid ""
"‘Yathodhi kho pana me cattaṃ vantaṃ muttaṃ pahīnaṃ paṭinissaṭṭhan’ti labhati "
"atthavedaṃ, labhati dhammavedaṃ, labhati dhammūpasaṃhitaṃ pāmojjaṃ;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn7:8-11.7"
msgid ""
"pamuditassa pīti jāyati, pītimanassa kāyo passambhati, passaddhakāyo sukhaṃ "
"vedeti, sukhino cittaṃ samādhiyati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya12"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "mn7:12.1"
msgid ""
"Sa kho so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃsīlo evaṃdhammo evaṃpañño sālīnañcepi "
"piṇḍapātaṃ bhuñjati vicitakāḷakaṃ anekasūpaṃ anekabyañjanaṃ, nevassa taṃ "
"hoti antarāyāya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn7:12.2"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, vatthaṃ saṅkiliṭṭhaṃ malaggahitaṃ acchodakaṃ āgamma "
"parisuddhaṃ hoti pariyodātaṃ, ukkāmukhaṃ vā panāgamma jātarūpaṃ parisuddhaṃ "
"hoti pariyodātaṃ;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn7:12.3"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃsīlo evaṃdhammo evaṃpañño sālīnañcepi "
"piṇḍapātaṃ bhuñjati vicitakāḷakaṃ anekasūpaṃ anekabyañjanaṃ, nevassa taṃ "
